definitions.definition: Something or someone which creates or makes something.
examples: Kenneth E. Iverson was the creator of APL.

definitions.definition: Ellipsis of content creator , someone who regularly produces and publishes content on social media , especially of a monetizable nature .
The deity that created the world.
A player who creates opportunities for their team to score goals ; a playmaker .

main_definition: Something or someone which creates or makes something.
secondary_definitions: ( social media ) Ellipsis of content creator , someone who regularly produces and publishes content on social media , especially of a monetizable nature .
